    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s an absolute dream! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in that gorgeous, showroom-floor condition. Not a scratch on it and the interior is totally spotless. It drives like a dream and has been so reliable. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make someone very happy. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
