    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant. This specimen retains its sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering a linear torque curve with no shaft play or boost leaks. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement with healthy synchros, paired with the factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal traction. The chassis is structurally immaculate, retaining all original VIN-matching body panels and factory-spec suspension geometry. Meticulously maintained with a documented timing belt service and compression numbers that mirror factory output. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
