    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was delivered. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, while the carpets and trim show zero signs of wear. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous, documented maintenance schedule performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle. Included are all original keys, the complete owner's manual set, and a comprehensive service history folder. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is an unparalleled find.",
      "price": 46500.0,
