      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of analog precision. It features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and VarioCam Plus timing, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral acoustic profile. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission is paired with a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers and zero-play bushings, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in concours-level Arctic Silver over a supple leather interior, this vehicle shows no signs of bore scoring and maintains perfect compression across all cylinders. A true collector-grade specimen with a meticulous service history.",
